verbose_text: To test whether IFT25 influences the stability of IFT-A and -B complexes, we created a vector based IFT25 miRNA strain called IFT25 miRNA (XREF_FIG A) and measured the protein level of the IFT-B components IFT46, IFT57 and IFT72 and the IFT-A components IFT43, IFT122 and IFT139 in these cells.
evidence: level of the IFT-B components IFT46, IFT57
